      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Reflects D-025 Departments (task-level access), D-027 publish gate, D-028 approval default OFF, D-029 collab doc delete, D-030 single-tier MVP (no custom domain / no white-label / Powered-by-Siapp always shown). Due dates optional. Client portal is READ-ONLY (no in-app chat in v1).",
